{"tid":919624,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"(大龜) 俄羅斯教育局官員：日本動畫中有摧毀國家的暗號","createTime":"2018-11-28T07:42:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-28T08:58:10.000Z","uid":49391,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e01cbf1aaf52d349f0cff720dac0658d2f56f484","tid":919624,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T07:42:05.000Z","msg":"日本動畫在世界各地的青少年中非常受歡迎，但是不少成年人還是對日本動畫不太喜歡，甚至還抱有一些成見。根據國外媒體Lenta.ru的報導，在俄羅斯新古比雪夫斯克的一所學校中，一名男學生因為手機上有&ldquo;動漫女孩&rdquo;的壁紙，就被老師公開處刑，最終又被強制刪除了該圖片。之後老師還通知了孩子的母親稱：&ldquo;日本的動畫圖片會破壞孩子的精神，所以應該禁止&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OS9AvBJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOS9AvBJ.jpg&h=dbfb66a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n為了確定日本動畫是否應該被禁止，該母親與俄羅斯聯邦教育科學局取得了聯繫詢問此事。教育局的一名女性負責人表示：&ldquo;學校並沒有權利沒收學生手機的權利，但動畫會對人產生不好的影響。動畫有第25幀(一般是24幀)，其中隱藏的隱秘信息可能會摧毀國家。&rdquo;另外該負責人還稱：&ldquo;歐洲已經禁止動畫很長時間了，動畫粉絲的集會（估計是漫展）像是邪教。&rdquo;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Uw1nU3u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUw1nU3u.jpg&h=108e824e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這位母親將這些話放到了網絡上，也是引起了大量的圍觀。對於這樣的解釋，不少網友表示雖然看到不少人說過動畫對孩子有不利影響，但還是第一次見到像這次這麼中二的發言。"},{"pid":"975c03b61ec681b04ff2f5f7602b53b259247a79","tid":919624,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T07:44:13.000Z","msg":"如果大龜去俄羅斯做官相信會撈得好掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n何必屈響連登傳教,真係大材小用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96e0468a9643d51fd9a4cb83e002573371fadab9","tid":919624,"uid":213441,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T07:50:50.000Z","msg":"watching anime is an MK behaviour"},{"pid":"bccc0c7316e1ae2abbfe8f0323f984999aeae4fe","tid":919624,"uid":33804,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T08:07:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SnoBfb6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSnoBfb6.jpg&h=c3ed58c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n想知戰鬥民族點睇呢套野"},{"pid":"83ccb07170c19c6bafdd6dd5f99d62168b65524b","tid":919624,"uid":98507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T08:19:45.000Z","msg":"幻之廿五幀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5835df169f52a72e0cad89158fbe997c42bd40f","tid":919624,"uid":41524,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T08:58:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/o3820753r201.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fo3820753r201.jpg&h=6d367ca2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如果部手機係放佢就冇事?"}]}